      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you aren't a doctor, but i'm just really scared to go to the a&e if it's just my anxiety acting up again. it's so expensive/tiring to go every time i feel like this. do you think there's a chance it's just stress? it feels a lot like the physical sensations i get when i'm having a panic attack.",
