      "content": "i hear you, but i just really don't want to go to the hospital if i don't have to. my doctor said last time that my anxiety is just very physical. can you just tell me what to look for to know for sure if it's just anxiety? if none of those extra things like jaw pain happen, can i just try to take a sedative and sleep it off? i'm hoping it's just a bad night.",
